'''Commercial waste''' consists of [[waste]] from premises used mainly for the purposes of a [[trade]] or [[business]] or for the purpose of [[sport]], [[recreation]], [[education]] or [[entertainment]], but excluding [[municipal waste|household]], [[agricultural waste|agricultural]] or [[industrial waste]].<ref>[http://www.wastenot.ie/pport/web/Classification/2/5.13.1?did=597726202&pageUrl=/Classification/2/5.7 Commercial Waste Definition] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070310211252/http://www.wastenot.ie/pport/web/Classification/2/5.13.1?did=597726202&pageUrl=%2FClassification%2F2%2F5.7 |date=2007-03-10 }} Waste Not - Waste Management Awareness for the South East of Ireland</ref>
